1.0.name: wordpress/wp-stacker
1.0.description: WP Stacker is a Wordpress plugin, with which you can post interesting links from Pocket (GetPocket.com) automatically on your blog - with autogenerated titles, discriptions and tags. You can customize the layout of the post completely. So you can save a lot of time, but show all your readers all your interesting links.
